author: @DeuDeoEgo
content:
To all those pathetic people going against Rio hosting Madonna: did you take into consideration that Madonna generated an estimated 50 to 60 million dollars of revenue for the state? Half the planet was talking about Madonna in Copacabana, she made the national news EVERYWHERE! That's great publicity for all parts involved!

Or do you believe that people just throw money for nothing in return? The state and the private sponsors know what they are doing when they fund a project.
